## üîó Endpoints (short reference)

- `GET /` ‚Äî service info (links to `/docs` and `/health`).
- `GET /health` ‚Äî JSON health status for monitoring.
- `GET /api/geo/area?lat=<lat>&lng=<lng>&radius=<r>` ‚Äî normalized coordinates.
- `GET /api/public-data/?lat=<lat>&lng=<lng>&radius=<r>` ‚Äî returns OSM elements, returns `[]` if upstream fails.
- `GET /api/telecom/?lat=<lat>&lng=<lng>` ‚Äî simulated telecom nodes (requires `X-API-Key` header: user or admin role).
- `GET /api/simulation/zone?lat=<lat>&lng=<lng>&radius=<r>` ‚Äî simulation endpoint (requires `X-API-Key` header: admin role).

